\omega_{\lambda\mathbf{x}+\mu\mathbf{y}}: A\ni a\mapsto \langle    \lambda\mathbf{x}+\mu\mathbf{y}|\pi(a)|\lambda\mathbf{x}+\mu\mathbf{y}\rangle / \lVert  \lambda\mathbf{x}+\mu\mathbf{y} \rVert^2\\  =\lvert \lambda\rvert^2 \omega_{\mathbf{x}}+ \lvert \mu\rvert^2 \omega_{\mathbf{y}} + \lambda^* \mu \langle\mathbf{x}|\pi(a) |\mathbf{y}\rangle + \lambda \mu^*\langle\mathbf{y}|\pi(a) |\mathbf{x}\rangle 
